task.summary:
Incremented Android version for next release.
Split collection and team code into separate files.
Initial team building code
Was missing module inclusion for split out team file

Split complex team edit view into multiple pages. Hand holding navigation back button for edit workflow since it really doesn't make sense in the traditional way.
Moved all team logic into a factory.

Basic cards too. Don't necessarily like how they're included, but it works in most places. No swiping between basic cards and characters in collection.
Tested without $watch on teams. Made no performance difference at all.
Icons for iOS build, first one sent in for review. Please say yes Apple.
